item.title: CoreUI PRO for React v5.0.0-rc.2
item.description: We’re thrilled to unveil CoreUI PRO for React v5.0.0-rc.2, bringing forth innovative features and crucial refinements that significantly elevate the development experience. Released on March 7, 2024, this version introduces enhanced capabilities and updates designed to streamline project development with CoreUI and React.
